api_list.description: This method return your IP and user agent.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://what-is-my-public-ip.p.rapidapi.com/v4/ip"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "what-is-my-public-ip.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
